<!doctype html>

<html>

	<head>
		<title>Help and FAQ</title>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<link href="/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">
		<link href="/css/bootstrap-grid.css" rel="stylesheet">
		<link href="/css/help.css" rel="stylesheet">
		<link href="/css/cancelNavbar.css" rel="stylesheet">

		<link rel="stylesheet"
			href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
		<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery.js"></script>
		<script src="/js/jquery-1.11.0.js"></script>
		<script src="/js/bootstrap.bundle.js"></script>
	</head>

	{{> cancelNavbar}}

	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="help-faq">
				<h1 align="left">Help and FAQ</h1>
			</div>

			<div class="leaderboard">
				<p id="leaderboard">
					<h3>Leaderboard:</h3>
					1) How to update ranking?
					<br />
					Ans: Press the camera button and open the camera to take a picture of you recycling.
					Upload the photo and wait for your score to update.

					<br /><br />

					2) How are you score?
					<br />
					Ans: You are being score by other people who are online to check if your
					picture is real and if they approve,your points are increase.

					<br /><br />

					3) How do I find my ranking?
					<br />
					Ans: Your ranking can be found in the Rank tab in the navigation bar.
					In there, you will see a "my rank" button above the leaderboard rankings which shows you your rank.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="discussion">
				<p id="discussion">
					<h3>Discussion:</h3>
					1) What do I find in "Discussion"?
					<br />
					Ans: You can find all sorts of topics on recycling. It serves to improve people's knowledge on
					recycling.
					You can also ask quesions on things you are not sure about.

					<br /><br />

					2) Do I need to login or have an account to use disccusion?
					<br />
					Ans: Yes, you need an account to do most things on Treeable

					<br /><br />

					3) How do I post a topic?
					<br />
					Ans: First Write a title on what your topic is, select a category to post in,
					write what your question or topic of disccusion is, and post.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="profile">
				<p id="profile">
					<h3>Profile:</h3>
					1) How do I change my username?
					<br />
					Ans: Go to Profile > setting > select change username.

					<br /><br />

					2) How do I link my social medias?<br />
					Ans: You can link your social media under Profile > Setting > Social Media.
					Now you can share your Gallery to your social media or search for friends!

					<br /><br />
				</p>
			</div>

		</div>
	</body>

</html>